overview.en: Qcash is a cryptocurrency with a value meant to mirror the value of the CNY(Chinese Yuan). The idea was to create a stable cryptocurrency that can be used like digital CNY. The price of 1 Qcash is 1 CNY. Users can use 1 CNY to buy 1 QC and then use QC to exchange BTC, LTC, ETH or other crypto assets. The max supply of QCash is 10,000,000,000 QC and circulating supply is 310,000,100 QC.
overview.zh: QC，全称为QCash，由QCASH基金会发行的独立数字货币，支持量子链智能合约代币和以太坊智能合约代币两种形式。1 QC的价格是1 CNY，用户可以使用1 CNY购买1个QC，然后使用QC交换BTC，LTC，ETH或其他数字资产。QCash的最大供应量为100亿 QC，流通量为310,000,100 QC。
